Class CourseDBStructure

  • java.lang.Object
    • CourseDBStructure
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CourseDBStructureInterface

    public class CourseDBStructure
extends java.lang.Object
implements CourseDBStructureInterface
    This class implements a hash table with buckets, creating an array of linked lists of CourseDBElements. Each CDE has a hash code that is generated from the crn. It adds CDEs to the data structure. If a linked list doesn't exist, it creates one and adds it to the hash table. If a linked list already exists for a given bucket, the CDE is added to the existing linked list.
